{"word":"Wool","slug":"wool","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Wool</b> Used for clothing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=52'>Lev 13:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=59'>Lev 13:59</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=13'>Pro 31:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=34&verse=3'>Eze 34:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=17'>Eze 44:17</a><br/> Prohibited in the priest's temple dress<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=17'>Eze 44:17</a><br/> Mixing of, with other fabrics forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=19'>Lev 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=11'>Deu 22:11</a><br/> Fleece of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=37'>Jdg 6:37</a><br/> First fleece of, belonged to the priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=4'>Deu 18:4</a>"}]}